ğŸ“Š Interactive Dashboard (Streamlit)

app.py provides:

Real-time port weather data by country

Interactive Folium map of port safety

Downloadable CSV reports

ğŸŒ Web Interface (Flask)

maritime_weather_ui.py allows users to fetch and view weather conditions for custom coordinates using the StormGlass API.

